Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行  社團教室太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星川  你也來啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,校園祭  我們要推出星空咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,準備的人手一直不足  還找不到你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才華的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是像水面上的蜻蜓一樣  生命短暫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前幾天  我喜歡的樂園突然解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽說團長的頭被折斷  無法東山再起...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,令人厭惡的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們的音樂已經永遠消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天我還想穿喪服  悼念那個樂團呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟敢連續兩次激怒我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,平山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次不是受傷而已  我要讓你連命都丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽見了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是你的心碎掉的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聖修伯里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8 \fs20}註：サン・テグジュぺリ (Saint-Exupery) 聖修伯里是童話"小王子"作者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雷穿！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你認得那男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是「音」樂團的歌手  叫做相島努
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才被攻擊的是團長平山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太過份了  手指骨都碎爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以部長的力量  不知道能不能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勉強還好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是他受到的打擊太大了  必須消除掉記憶才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不...  我一直在想...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把記憶消除掉真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣真的對這個人好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在說甚麼天真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不消除記憶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個人可能發瘋  或是經常做惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣也好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道嗎  星川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消除掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...  可以瞭解他想說的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個男人到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明有打中他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畜牲...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我記住  那個臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是可以直接了結你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是你還有可利用價值
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我給你新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就接下這個力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是  有夠麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以上是今天為止的調查進度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老實說  這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們社團的星空咖啡廳  是趕不上學園祭的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三輪阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咖啡廳制服製作得還順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新開  秋天風景的裝飾品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過人手真的不足呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼就抓那個閒閒的  在那兒偷窺的人怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下  為甚麼找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是三輪阪的同學....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也是人數不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來找三輪阪幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請問可以借她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡啦  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起  讓妳等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也剛剛才到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天喬姐姐社團的  星空咖啡廳真熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真琴  今天就別太花哨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把這個解下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉  我睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你久等了  我換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真好  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百瀨  你是何時加入天文部的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不在乎我們社團生死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我送光一回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天真是謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,陪班上的笨蛋累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三輪阪！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳  你在幹甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳果然來了  臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這女人在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想救人的話  就到車站前的 Live House
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡  都是我的錯  如果那時候把他打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛...  那傢伙是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百瀨  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三輪阪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被抓走了  我去追他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你暫時能撐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勉強還行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好  等喬他們回來了  你幫我轉告他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地點是車站前的 Live House
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要怎樣對那女人報仇  就隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉  真言美她...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亮  拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我走  甚麼都不要問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三輪阪在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她只是引妳出來的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說甚麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒想到妳會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒辦法  死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很少使用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看妳身材這麼高大  裡面卻如此狹小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這只是剛開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近都運動不足呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放開小泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道你的意志  可以貫穿我們的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉  別把外人捲入火者與光狩的糾紛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳不想多流無益的血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言靈只限於這次使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人是小泉妳的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起  我一直沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都在擔心  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二個也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們的實力只有這一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒禮貌的人  我們只是太大意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉  最後的對手是妳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太令人失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會吧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且妳的記憶被抹失過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳不記得自己是為何而戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比使魔還不如
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三輪阪也...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是怎麼了  渾身是傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是大姐為了救她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去車站前的 Live House 還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很不妙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳很喜歡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我想聽的...  不是這樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會讓妳輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒中...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都沒有生命危險的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的  那些人很健壯的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉  我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不想看妳一個人獨自痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算發生無可抗拒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想減輕妳的痛苦  與命運的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在醫院遇到平山
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他說無論如何  會繼續搞音樂下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道妳要找我談甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想消除我們的記憶是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算不願意  現在的我...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也無法可走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啊  妳下手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.11,0:24:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.58,0:24:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸  媽媽  小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.91,0:24:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都一直假裝不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.79,0:24:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為甚麼消除我的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.86,0:24:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.86,0:24:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是為甚麼與光狩作戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.47,0:24:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把我的記憶還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.64,0:25:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.84,0:25:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起  突然找你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白天...  我去看大家的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.85,0:25:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每個都失去了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.85,0:25:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新開  星川  鏡花也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.46,0:25:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們...  是為甚麼在戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.47,0:25:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到光狩附在後籐身上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.21,0:25:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得他們不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.01,0:25:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想打倒那樣子  利用人類的寂寞的光狩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.21,0:25:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以為自己是憑自己的意志  為創造自己的位置而作戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是看來並不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.56,0:26:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次的事情讓我察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.09,0:26:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是因為小泉妳  才決定一起作戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.90,0:26:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,與光狩的戰爭  可能不會輕易結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.70,0:26:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是小泉背負的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.05,0:26:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是我能夠與妳一起擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.84,0:26:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我願意作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.39,0:26:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.12,0:26:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我喜歡小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.19,0:26:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.60,0:26:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於說出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.87,0:26:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喜歡妳  小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.28,0:26:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起  亮
